    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies the manner for transmitting IPv4 datagrams over an ATM data link, both in a default manner and in the presence of flow labelling via Ipsilon Flow Management Protocol [IFMP].  This document provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
